      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">David has been planting in Las Cruces for over 19 years. He knows which species thrive at this elevation, which ones need afternoon shade, and which ones are a waste of money in our soil. Every planting comes with the right irrigation hookup and soil amendment so it actually establishes.</p>
